		<item>
		<title>HAPPY BIRTHDAY TWIST!!  Have a free eBook!</title>
		<link>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2013/11/17/happy-birthday-twist-have-a-free-ebook/</link>
					<comments>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2013/11/17/happy-birthday-twist-have-a-free-ebook/#comments</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2013 20:00:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Twisty things]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Clockwork Twist]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CWTwist]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[ebook]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Emily Thompson]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[free ebook]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[neo-Victorian]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[smashwords]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[steampunk]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[victoriana]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Waking]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://clockworktwist.com/?p=1123</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Oh, they grow up so fast! Well, it&#8217;s official.  My beautiful boy is 3 years old today.  Well, the series is, anyway.  Now it&#8217;s time to party!  Break out the wine!  Light the birthday candles!  Start singing out of tune!  Run in terror from the skanky clown that some idiot hired.  Put on your silly [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-1257" alt="" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093542.jpg" width="672" height="504" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093542.jpg 3264w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093542-300x225.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093542-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px" /></p>
<p>Oh, they grow up so fast!</p>
<p>Well, it&#8217;s official.  My beautiful boy is 3 years old today.  Well, the series is, anyway.  Now it&#8217;s time to party!  Break out the wine!  Light the birthday candles!  Start singing out of tune!  Run in terror from the skanky clown that some idiot hired.  Put on your silly paper hats, and let&#8217;s all toast our favorite little clockmaker&#8217;s good fortune!<a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-2-2.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1252 alignright" alt="By Betsy Lastar" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-snapshot.jpg" width="258" height="188" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-snapshot.jpg 615w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-snapshot-300x217.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px" /></a></p>
<p>But best of all, it&#8217;s time to unwrap the presents!  As promised, the eBook of the Waking 2nd Edition  will be FREE all day today, on <a href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/292403" target="_blank">Smashwords.com</a></p>
<p>(Not Amazon.  They&#8217;re no fun.)</p>
<h4 style="text-align:center;"><a href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/292403" target="_blank">Go grab a shiny new copy right now</a>!</h4>
<p>Share the link with your loved ones!  Share it with your enemies!  Share it with your postman!  Don&#8217;t let anyone miss out.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-1258" style="margin-bottom:20px;" alt="" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093358.jpg" width="229" height="305" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093358.jpg 2448w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093358-225x300.jpg 225w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093358-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 229px) 100vw, 229px" /></p>
<p><span style="line-height:1.5;">If you&#8217;ve already got a copy of the 1st Edition, you can download the new version for free as well.  Just follow the </span><a style="line-height:1.5;" href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/292403" target="_blank">link</a><span style="line-height:1.5;">, then scroll down and click the &#8220;download&#8221; link for the format you&#8217;d like.  On the following page, click the link for today&#8217;s date, Nov 17th.  </span></p>
<p><span style="line-height:1.5;">If you&#8217;ve missed the party, and are reading this after the 17th, you can still get the new version for free at any point, just so long as you already bought the eBook on </span><a style="line-height:1.5;" href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/292403" target="_blank">Smashwords</a><span style="line-height:1.5;">.</span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1256 alignright" alt="" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093501.jpg" width="342" height="256" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093501.jpg 3264w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093501-300x225.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/20131117_093501-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 342px) 100vw, 342px" /><br />
If you bought your Kindle eBook on Amazon, you should be getting an e-mail from them soon.</p>
<p>Follow the instructions in their email to get the updated version.  Or you could get the <a href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/292403" target="_blank">Smashwords</a> version today, as well.  Seriously, why not?</p>
<p><span style="line-height:1.5;">And don&#8217;t forget to submit any photos or fan-art, or anything you do to celebrate Twist&#8217;s big day!  (Comment here, Facebook, Goodreads, #CWTwist, whatever)  I&#8217;ll add everything I get to a special after-party post.  Here&#8217;s a super cute little comic strip I got just last night!  Thanks Betsy!! (click to enlarge)</span></p>
<p><a title="Twist birthday comic by Betsy Lastar" href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-3-2.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1251 alignleft" alt="By Betsy Lastar" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-3-2.jpg" width="702" height="952" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-3-2.jpg 702w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-3-2-221x300.jpg 221w" sizes="(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px" /></a><br />
<a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-1-2.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1248" alt="By Betsy Lastar" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-1-close-up.jpg" width="718" height="626" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-1-close-up.jpg 718w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/twist-1-close-up-300x261.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 718px) 100vw, 718px" /></a></p>
<p>Isn&#8217;t that just darling?  I also want to say thank you to everyone for celebrating with me!  This is the first year that I&#8217;ve thrown Twist much of a birthday party. I&#8217;m sure he would go bright pink with embarrassment at all of this hullabaloo.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
					<wfw:commentRss>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2013/11/17/happy-birthday-twist-have-a-free-ebook/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
			<slash:comments>2</slash:comments>
		
		
			</item>
		<item>
		<title>FREE ebook, and paperback giveaway for Twist&#8217;s B-day!</title>
		<link>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2013/10/27/free-ebook-and-paperback-giveaway-for-twists-b-day/</link>
					<comments>http://clockworktwist.com/blog/2013/10/27/free-ebook-and-paperback-giveaway-for-twists-b-day/#comments</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2013 17:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[indie publishing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Twisty things]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[book giveaway]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Clockwork Twist]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CWTwist]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[ebook]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Emily Thompson]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[free ebook]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[neo-Victorian]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[steampunk]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Waking]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://clockworktwist.com/?p=795</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Good news, everyone!  No, I haven&#8217;t created a new doomsday device, but I will be doing two book giveaways in November!!  As you may have read in a previous post, Twist&#8217;s birthday will be on November 17th.  What better way to celebrate than with gifts to my marvelous fans?  Well, yeah, okay.  Adorable Steampunk cupcakes [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://bakingdom.com/2010/12/tootsie-roll-modeling-chocolate-on-steampunk-cupcakes.html" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignright" alt="So cute!!!  Click for the recipe." src="http://www.bakingdom.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Close-up-Steampunk-Cupcake.jpg" width="230" height="230" /></a>Good news, everyone!  No, I haven&#8217;t created a new doomsday device, but I will be doing two book giveaways in November!!  As you may have read in <a title="Twist will be 3 years old on Nov 17th!  Mark the date!" href="http://clockworktwist.com/2013/06/24/bday/" target="_blank">a previous post</a>, Twist&#8217;s birthday will be on November 17th.  What better way to celebrate than with gifts to my marvelous fans?  Well, yeah, okay.  <a href="http://bakingdom.com/2010/12/tootsie-roll-modeling-chocolate-on-steampunk-cupcakes.html" target="_blank">Adorable Steampunk cupcakes</a> are probably another great way to celebrate.  I know I want some!</p>
<p>Now, to book business!</p>
<p>The first giveaway will be on Goodreads.  I&#8217;ll be launching a new 2nd edition of Waking, with bonus content, on December 16th.  This new edition will be essentially the same as the first, but with the bonus of the first few chapters of <a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/" target="_blank">Trick</a> added at the back.  Because you know, <a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/" target="_blank">Trick</a> is coming very, very soon&#8230;  If you&#8217;ve already got your copy of Waking, don&#8217;t despair!  I&#8217;ll also be posting the same preview chapters on my site as well, starting in December.  But, If you don&#8217;t have your paperback copy yet, or you want a new shiny copy for free, go and <a href="http://www.goodreads.com/giveaway/show/62625-clockwork-twist---book-one-waking" target="_blank">sign up on Goodreads</a>, starting on the 1st of November!</p>
<p>But wait, there&#8217;s more!  I&#8217;m also going to price the 2nd edition of the eBook for FREE all day on Twist&#8217;s birthday, the 17th.  The content of the eBook 2nd edition will be the same as a the paperback, complete with the new chapters.  And best of all, if you already have a copy of the eBook, you&#8217;ll be able to download the new version for FREE!   I&#8217;ll give instructions when the days get closer, so keep an eye on the blog/<a href="http://www.facebook.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">facebook</a>/<a href="http://twitter.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">twitter</a>/<a href="http://cwtwist.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">tumblr</a>/whatever!</p>
<p>To some up, here are the dates to add you your calendar:</p>
<ul>
<li>Nov 1st &#8211; Nov 30th, <a href="http://www.goodreads.com/giveaway/show/62625-clockwork-twist---book-one-waking" target="_blank">Paperback giveaway sign up</a>.</li>
<li>Nov 17th &#8211; Twist is 3 years old!!  And, free eBook all day!</li>
<li>Dec 15th, 2nd edition of Waking launched, and the first preview chapter of <a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/" target="_blank">Trick</a> posted on the site.</li>
</ul>
<p>Oh, I&#8217;m so excited!</p>
<p>As if that wasn&#8217;t enough all ready, I&#8217;m also going to make an appearance at a local Author Fair, this Saturday.  If you&#8217;re in the San Jose area, come say hi!  And find out what other literary gems Silicon Valley is hiding&#8230;</p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://sjpl.org/authorfair" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="" src="http://sjpl.org/sites/all/files/resize/userimages/AF%20flyer-600x181.jpg" width="600" height="181" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
